sections.heading: Council; minutes of meetings; reports
sections.text: The Legislative Council shall keep complete minutes of its meetings and shall submit electronically periodical reports to the members of the Legislature.SourceLaws 1937, c. 118, ยง 9, p. 424;C.S.Supp.,1941, ยง 50-509;R.S.1943, ยง 50-413;Laws 1949, c. 168, ยง 7, p. 4
